## Build / Test Commands
- install: `pnpm install`
- dev: `pnpm dev`
- build: `pnpm build`
- test: `pnpm test`

## 目录说明
- `app/`：前端页面
- `public/`：静态资源
- `scripts/`：巡检与自动化脚本

